{"tid":2104484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唐山5.1級地震　天津北京震感強烈","createTime":"2020-07-12T04:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T04:39:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"177daf07ab4b09b912af7fb81c808d6fb8eb4bb8","tid":2104484,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200712/photo/bkn-20200712070022307-0712_00952_001_01p.jpg?20200712113228\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200712%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200712070022307-0712_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20200712113228&h=9e6a03cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唐山大地震<br />\n<br />\n中國地震台網測定，河北唐山市古冶區周日（12日）早上6時38分發生黎克特制5.1級地震，震源深度10公里。天津距離震央132公里，有網民指天津、北京震感強烈。約半小時後，同一地區附近再發生至少兩次2級或以上餘震。<br />\n<br />\n地震消息一出，不少網民紛紛表示關注，並提到河北多地、天津、北京均有震感，其中天津更有網民聲稱從睡夢中被震醒，形容是近幾年震感最強的一次。另有人指地震時整張床都在搖晃，燈也有晃動。​​​​<br />\n<br />\n約半小時後，同一地區附近發生至少兩次分別2級及2.2級餘震。中國地震台網指，震央周邊200公里內，於近5年已發生17次3級以上地震，而今次屬最大震級。鐵路部門隨後表示，地震發生後已啟動應急預案，暫停途經該地區的旅客列車，派員檢查鐵路設施。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200712/bkn-20200712070022307-0712_00952_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"10b52a926de8e6c5a8dd3b9e3afadf10b8494378","tid":2104484,"uid":2501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"邊條女用完震蛋唔記得熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6b773d0ac8901be061750fd90eb2d3492bf37f","tid":2104484,"uid":247847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:35:24.000Z","msg":"5.1<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過可以再高級D<br />\n7.1都唔錯<br />\n9.1就最好啦"},{"pid":"fca630e3968cfbae5786e4893a29cd379ce0871c","tid":2104484,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b52a926de8e6c5a8dd3b9e3afadf10b8494378","tid":2104484,"uid":2501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"邊條女用完震蛋唔記得熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"條女叫地球，唔怪之得早排又怪叫、又一直出水，原來玩緊震蛋，幾時玩中出?"},{"pid":"b22698d5fb43f5cf8e48fa55412304f3bc9073e5","tid":2104484,"uid":106683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:35:45.000Z","msg":"最好係15.1"},{"pid":"7ec5fd6b071ddc3f2961f1eb2bb109fbbfdb9d5a","tid":2104484,"uid":266342,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"先得個5.1地震<br />\n呢個天都根本就偏袒支那<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以俾返1976年嘅時候嗰種威力再加10倍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6608178533ad9eef668e62c9e9cb18924aebec","tid":2104484,"uid":68987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"其實點解一個國家同一時間可以有咁多問題<br />\n又水災又蝗蟲又病毒<br />\n仲要同印度台灣衝突<br />\n呢排仲要挑釁哈薩克斯坦"}]}